Install LAMP 
Reference link: 
http://wiki.ubuntu.org.cn/Apache

APACHE
--installation
apt-get install apache2 
--Restart Service
sudo /etc/init.d/apache2 restart
--Comments
a2enmod
a2dismod
a2ensite
a2dissite
--enable rewrite feature
a2enmod rewrite 	
--root of website document
/var/www
--tips
all enabled module and site are locate in /etc/apache2/
edit webiste cofiguration for root directionary, port etc..
--open question
how can prevent user acess to the web files?

PHP
--installation
apt-get install php5 php5-gd php5-mysql
(restart apache to enable php)
--cofiguration
open safe_mode and time zone in php.ini

MYSQL
--installation
apt-get install mysql-server mysql-client


